data.title: I/O Fund Called the Bitcoin Selloff: What Liquidity & DXY Data Predict Next
data.description: In August, the I/O Fund warned that Bitcoin was entering a high-risk phase as global liquidity stalled, and sentiment patterns flashed caution. Since then, Bitcoin has fallen more than -35%. In this article, follow up with the liquidity issues that are roiling risk assets, including Bitcoin. As investors will see, the technical outlook has shifted, increasing risk that a larger top could be in.
